# SKILL: React Component Patterns (MUI)
# Applies to: client/src/**

## Component Structure — Always Follow This

Every React component lives in `client/src/` and follows this layout:

```
client/src/
  components/
    common/          ← shared, reusable (Button, Modal, Table, MediaPicker)
    layout/          ← Header, Sidebar, Footer, PageWrapper
  pages/
    admin/           ← admin-only pages
    customer/        ← customer-facing pages
  features/
    <feature>/       ← co-located feature components (cart, product, checkout)
```

## Component Rules

- **One component per file** — no barrel exports with multiple components
- **Named exports only** — never default export for components
- **Props interface at top** — document all props with JSDoc or PropTypes
- **No business logic in components** — call hooks/services, never raw API calls
- **No inline styles** — use MUI `sx` prop or `styled()` only
- **No hardcoded colors** — always use MUI theme tokens (`primary.main`, `grey.500`)

## MUI Patterns — Always Use

### Theme-aware styling
```jsx
// CORRECT — uses theme
<Box sx={{ color: 'primary.main', bgcolor: 'background.paper', p: 2 }}>

// WRONG — hardcoded
<Box sx={{ color: '#1976d2', backgroundColor: '#fff', padding: '16px' }}>
```

### Responsive layout
```jsx
// Always use MUI breakpoints, never raw media queries
<Grid container spacing={{ xs: 1, sm: 2, md: 3 }}>
  <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
```

### Standard page component shape
```jsx
// pages/customer/ProductListPage.jsx
import { Container, Typography, Box } from '@mui/material';
import { useProducts } from '../../features/product/hooks/useProducts';
import { ProductGrid } from '../../features/product/ProductGrid';

export function ProductListPage() {
  const { products, isLoading, error } = useProducts();

  if (isLoading) return <PageLoader />;
  if (error) return <ErrorBoundaryFallback error={error} />;

  return (
    <Container maxWidth="xl">
      <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom>
        Products
      </Typography>
      <ProductGrid products={products} />
    </Container>
  );
}
```

### Standard feature component shape
```jsx
// features/product/ProductCard.jsx
import { Card, CardMedia, CardContent, Typography, Button } from '@mui/material';

export function ProductCard({ product, onAddToCart }) {
  return (
    <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
      <CardMedia
        component="img"
        image={product.images?.[0]?.url ?? '/placeholder.png'}
        alt={product.name}
        sx={{ aspectRatio: '1', objectFit: 'cover' }}
      />
      <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
        <Typography variant="h6" noWrap>{product.name}</Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
          ₹{product.salePrice ?? product.price}
        </Typography>
      </CardContent>
      <Button onClick={() => onAddToCart(product.id)} fullWidth variant="contained">
        Add to Cart
      </Button>
    </Card>
  );
}
```

## Component Review Checklist
- [ ] No raw API calls inside component — uses hook or service
- [ ] No hardcoded colors or spacing — uses MUI theme tokens
- [ ] Loading and error states handled
- [ ] Mobile responsive — uses MUI breakpoints
- [ ] No inline `style={{}}` — uses `sx` prop
- [ ] Images have `alt` text
- [ ] Buttons have accessible labels
- [ ] Named export (not default)

